# Images folder
Place your blog post images in this directory.

## Recommended structure:
- `/images/posts/` - Blog post images
- `/images/covers/` - Cover images for posts
- `/images/gallery/` - Photo galleries

## Image optimization tips:
- Use WebP format when possible for better compression
- Resize images to appropriate dimensions (max 1920px width for covers)
- Compress images before uploading to improve page load speed